replies.body:
I've got to agree, Pyke really feels like a good addition to LoL. He's interesting, exciting to play, and feels somewhat niche. The times I've found myself playing him (in ARAM) I've had fun, even if it's turned into a stomp on my team. I can't see myself seriously playing him in the future, but I can appreciate how well he turned out.

Good job Riot!
{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}
